description:
Final part of the current Nikolai Dante storyline and the last Dante story illustrated by John Burns. Also, the return of three classic Dredd villains in Day of Chaos.

Cover: James McKay (Flesh)

  • Judge Dredd - Day of Chaos - Eve of Destruction (part 15) (John Wagner - Henry Flint)
  • The Zaucer of Zilk (part 5) (Al Ewing and Brendan McCarthy - Brendan McCarthy)
  • Flesh - Midnight Cowboys (part 6) (Pat Mills - James McKay)
  • Age of the Wolf 2 (part 8) (Alec Worley - Jon Davis-Hunt)
  • Nikolai Dante - The Dante Gambit (part 6 - final part) (Robbie Morrison - John Burns)
name: Prog 1779
